<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Link Expired - FreelanceHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .exp-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 42px 34px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 440px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .exp-icon {
      width: 70px; height: 70px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      font-size: 1.8rem; color: #fff;
    }
    .exp-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800;
      color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .exp-card p {
      color: #64748b; font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .steps-box {
      background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px;
      text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .steps-box h4 {
      font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: #374151; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .step-row {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.84rem; color: #64748b;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 22px; height: 22px;
      background: #6c63ff; color: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ban-warn {
      background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .ban-warn p { color: #991b1b; font-size: 0.82rem; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="auth-body">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;padding:20px;">
    <div class="exp-card">

      <div class="exp-icon"><i class="fas fa-link-slash"></i></div>
      <h2>Link Expire Ho Gaya!</h2>
      <p>
        Aapka verification link <strong>expire</strong> ho gaya hai ya <strong>invalid</strong> hai.<br>
        Neeche diye steps follow karein.
      </p>

      <!-- Ban warning -->
      <div class="ban-warn">
        <p>
          <strong>⚠️ Warning:</strong> Agar abhi bhi verify nahi kiya, account
          <strong>ban ho sakta hai</strong>. Jaldi karein!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Steps -->
      <div class="steps-box">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-info-circle" style="color:#6c63ff;margin-right:5px;"></i> Aage kya karein?</h4>
        <div class="step-row">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <span>Email inbox check karein — aur ek warning email aa sakti hai</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <span>Agar account ban nahi hua, support se contact karein</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row" style="margin-bottom:0;">
          <span class="step-num" style="background:#22c55e;">3</span>
          <span>Ya fresh register karein agar account available hai</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buttons -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
          <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Naya Account Banayein
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:support@freelancehub.com" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Support Se Contact Karein
        </a>
        <a href="/auth/login"
           style="font-size:0.83rem;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;margin-top:6px;">
          ← Login Page
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
